Class RoomController

java.lang.Object
com.erahotel.era_backend.controller.RoomController
@CrossOrigin("*") @RestController @RequestMapping("/api/rooms") public class RoomController extends Object
REST controller for managing rooms.

Provides endpoints for creating, retrieving, updating, and deleting rooms, as well as managing room reservations.

Author:
Alwin Roble
